<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Bayesian phylogram inferred from 28 S (region D 2 - D 3) sequence data aligned by secondary structure. Bayesian analysis runtime = 736,000 generations (25 % burnin). Branch support: Bayesian posterior probabilities / bootstrap (1,000 replicates). (-) indicates bootstrap support below 60." , "Figure 5. Biroia fuscicornis Cameron, light morph a lateral head b dorsal head c lateral mesosoma d dorsal mesosoma e dorsal metasoma." , ". Figure 3. Biroia fuscicornis Cameron, dark morph a lateral habitus b fore wing." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11199" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11218" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11216" .

